public class JsElementalBase
extends JavaScriptObject
implements Mappable, Indexable, IndexableInt, IndexableNumber, Settable, SettableInt, SettableNumber

All Elemental classes must extend this base class, mixes in support for Indexable, Settable, Mappable.
